node.text: My girl Perdita after a nice soak. Just helping her get that old skin off. She looks amazing. I always have to say we do not help snakes shed unless they have stuck shed on them. We always allow them to try to shed on their own. Certain times of the year when we have the AC on from a hot day or the heat on when it’s a cool day it can dry the air and some animals have more issues shedding. That’s when we help them. Never remove a snakes skin before they are ready to shed. It can be very bad for them. #reticsofinstagram #snakeshed #shed #shedding #snake #reptile #reptarium #brianbarcyzk

node.text: Here’s the moment that the virgin birth happened with my Green Anaconda. Of course it’s call Parthenogenesis and is a rare occurrence when a female gives birth with no male fertilization.  One of the coolest things i have ever had happen while working with reptiles. #greenanaconda #anaconda #babysnakes #miracle #birth #snake #reptile #reptarium #brianbarcyzk

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by B R I A N   B A R C Z Y K on August 19, 2021.

node.text: Today’s Vlog is insane. We found out that Aries our male Anaconda is actually a female. But more insane is “she” had a live virgin birth! We got one perfectly healthy baby Green Anaconda from her. She had never been in with a male her entire life. It’s called Parthenogenesis and is very rare. We caught the birth on film and you can watch it today over on my Vlog channel. One of the most amazing things i have ever seen. #greenanaconda #anaconda #virginbirth #parthnogenisis #babysnake #babyanaconda #reptarium #miracle #brianbarcyzk
